description: Retrieves the location of stored game session logs for a specified game session on Amazon GameLift managed fleets. When a game session is terminated, Amazon GameLift automatically stores the logs in Amazon S3 and retains them for 14 days. Use this URL to download the logs. All APIs by task.

parameters.name: GameSessionId
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the game session to get logs for.

nested_items.name: PreSignedUrl
nested_items.description: Location of the requested game session logs, available for download. This URL is valid for 15 minutes, after which S3 will reject any download request using this URL. You can request a new URL any time within the 14-day period that the logs are retained.
